{"tid":2184813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國防部: 中共未放棄攻打台灣.  中國的核彈頭數量將增加最少一倍","createTime":"2020-09-02T00:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T04:05:38.000Z","uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"417ed0472f4d547eeb6fa0c8c0f11d2246a14f25","tid":2184813,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:38:44.000Z","msg":"2020-09-02 HKT 07:36<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部發表年度中國軍力報告，預料中國的核彈頭數量，未來10年會由現時的大約200枚，增加最少一倍，並已經接近擁有發動海陸空核打擊的能力。<br />\n.....<br />\n五角大樓的報告又指出，<strong>北京仍未放棄透過武力統一台灣</strong>，解放軍繼續加強準備，以防止台灣獨立，<strong>並在必要時武力攻台</strong>，解放軍可能採取海空封鎖、有限軍力或強制選項、空中與導彈攻擊、入侵台灣的行動路線，又指解放軍認為可信賴的武力威脅，對維持政治進展與防止台獨是至關重要。<br />\n<br />\n五角大樓認為，兩岸軍力失衡情況持續擴大，認為基於台灣關係法與六項保證，持續對台軍售，有助確保台灣擁有自我防衛能力。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547338-20200902.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547338-20200902.htm&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=75832de2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547338-20200902.htm&h=fe803c7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547338-20200902.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d97f990be8ffae1ae9aee12136f42dd699e46ad2","tid":2184813,"uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:39:18.000Z","msg":"小學雞打台灣, 唔奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe77f59966bffbedf063d7f23bfd070f6df968a","tid":2184813,"uid":19126,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:40:54.000Z","msg":"成大段野重點係最後果段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有生意做，又有個盟友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34197e0e74e4e7220a0167418cc8e6a48ce137b","tid":2184813,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe77f59966bffbedf063d7f23bfd070f6df968a